lead_paragraph: Paris St Germain have what it takes to reach rhe Champions League final this season after three consecutive quarter-final exits, Argentine winner Angel Di Maria said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: PSG Equipped to Reach Champions League Final, Says Di Maria
